Expunge Both
Create Both

IMAPAccount work
Host $MAIL_WORK_IMAP_HOST
User $MAIL_WORK_USERNAME
Pass $MAIL_WORK_PASSWORD

IMAPStore work-remote
Account work

MaildirStore work-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path $HOME/Mail/work/
Inbox $HOME/Mail/work/Inbox

Channel work
Master :work-remote:
Slave :work-local:
Patterns *
SyncState *

